{"slug":"sirkuler-25-0249eng","reference":"Sirkuler_25_0249ENG","gazette":"WTO Notification","title":"Regarding the notification regarding the planned revision of the European Commission steel safeguard measure","date":"17 Mart 2025","bodyHtml":"<p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">The European Commission notified the World Trade Organisation on the proposed revision of the steel safeguard measure on 10 March 2025.</font></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">The relevant revisions are expected to be effective as of April 1, 2025.</font></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; outline: 0px !important;\"><a href=\"https://docs.wto.org/dol2fe/Pages/SS/directdoc.aspx?filename=T:/G/SG/N10EU1S20.docx&amp;Open=True\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgba(var(--bs-link-color-rgb),var(--bs-link-opacity,1)); text-decoration-line: underline; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">Click here for notifications and country quotas.</font></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">According to the notification, there will be an average decrease of 15 percent in the three-month quarterly quotas allocated to Türkiye in some product categories.</font></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">There will also be some changes in the categories in which Türkiye is subject to measures. Türkiye will not be subject to measures in the following categories;</font></p><ul style=\"padding-left: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; outline: 0px !important;\"><li style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold; outline: 0px !important;\">Category 1B&nbsp;</span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;: 7212 60 00&nbsp;</font></li><li style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold; outline: 0px !important;\">Category 8</span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;: Hot rolled stainless steel sheets and strips: 7219 11 00, 7219 12 10, 7219 12 90, 7219 13 10, 7219 13 90, 7219 14 10, 7219 14 90, 7219 22 10, 7219 22 90, 7219 23 00, 7219 24 00, 7220 11 00, 7220 12 00</font></li><li style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold; outline: 0px !important;\">Category 3A</span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;: 7209 16 10, 7209 17 10, 7209 18 10, 7209 26 10, 7209 27 10, 7209 28 10.</font></li></ul><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">The table of changes in the categories in which Türkiye has a country quota is as follows.</font></p><table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"caption-side: bottom; border: none; outline: 0px !important;\"><tbody style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; outline: 0px !important;\"><tr style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; height: 42.05pt; outline: 0px !important;\"><td width=\"380\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 284.7pt; height: 42.05pt; outline: 0px !important;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: normal; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">Product groups allocated Country Quota to Türkiye and 01.04.2025-30.06.2025 Single Quarter Quota (tons)</font><o:p style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"></o:p></p></td><td width=\"85\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-top: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: none; padding: 0cm 